## Layer 1: Config Files (The Heart)

Six **horizon-agnostic** config files define the system's fixed rules:

| File | Role | Key Exports |
|------|------|-------------|
| [setup_pattern_matrix_config.py](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/setup_pattern_matrix_config.py) | Setup↔Pattern affinity, classification rules, validation modifiers | `SETUP_PATTERN_MATRIX` — ~18 setups with PRIMARY/CONFIRMING/CONFLICTING patterns |
| [strategy_matrix_config.py](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/strategy_matrix_config.py) | Strategy DNA: fit indicators, scoring rules, market cap filters | `STRATEGY_MATRIX` — ~10 strategies (swing, day trading, trend following, value, etc.) |
| [confidence_config.py](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/confidence_config.py) | Confidence calculation: ADX bands, volume modifiers, setup floors | `CONFIDENCE_CONFIG` — global + per-horizon adjustments |
| [technical_score_config.py](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/technical_score_config.py) | Technical indicator scoring (40+ metrics) | `METRIC_REGISTRY` + scoring functions |
| [fundamental_score_config.py](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/fundamental_score_config.py) | Fundamental metric scoring with horizon participation | `METRIC_REGISTRY` + `HORIZON_FUNDAMENTAL_WEIGHTS` |
| [master_config.py](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/master_config.py) | Horizon-specific overrides, gates, execution rules, risk mgmt | `MASTER_CONFIG` — the envelope wrapping all 6 files |

### How [master_config.py](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/master_config.py) Wraps Everything

```
MASTER_CONFIG = {
    "global": {
        "entry_gates": { structural, opportunity },
        "execution_rules": { volatility_guards, structure_validation, sl_distance, target_proximity },
        "risk_management": { base_risk_pct, max_position_pct, position_sizing },
        "strategy_preferences": { priorities, blocked setups, conflict resolution }
    },
    "horizons": {
        "intraday": { gates (override), rr_gates, execution, pillar_weights, time_estimation },
        "short_term": { ... },
        "long_term": { ... },
        "multibagger": { ... }
    }
}
```

### Setup Config Structure (Per Setup in `SETUP_PATTERN_MATRIX`)

```
"MOMENTUM_BREAKOUT": {
    "patterns":       { PRIMARY, CONFIRMING, CONFLICTING },
    "classification_rules": { technical_conditions, fundamental_conditions },
    "default_priority": 90,
    "default_confidence_floor": 55,
    "context_requirements": { technical: {adx, trendStrength, ...}, fundamental: {required, roe, ...} },
    "horizon_overrides": { intraday: {...}, short_term: {...}, long_term: {...}, multibagger: {...} },
    "validation_modifiers": { penalties: {...}, bonuses: {...} },
    "min_pattern_quality": 7.0,
    "min_setup_score": 80,
    "setup_type": "breakout"
}
```

