## Layer 2: Extraction (Config → Query API)

### ConfigExtractor ([config_extractor.py](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/config_extractor.py))

Pre-extracts all config sections at initialization into typed [ConfigSection](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/config_extractor.py#45-52) objects:

```python
class ConfigExtractor:
    def __init__(self, master_config, horizon):
        self.extract_all()  # Pre-fetch everything
    
    def extract_all(self):
        self.extract_confidence_sections()   # From confidence_config.py
        self.extract_global_sections()       # From master_config.global
        self.extract_horizon_sections()      # From master_config.horizons[horizon]
        self.extract_setup_sections()        # From setup_pattern_matrix
        self.extract_strategy_sections()     # From strategy_matrix
        self.extract_risk_sections()         # From master_config risk management
        self.extract_gate_sections()         # Gate hierarchy: global → horizon → setup
        self.extract_matrix_sections()       # Full matrix data (patterns, physics)
```

### QueryOptimizedExtractor ([query_optimized_extractor.py](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py))

Wraps [ConfigExtractor](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/config_extractor.py#58-1256) with **85 type-safe query methods**, organized in 7 categories:

| Category | Example Methods |
|----------|-----------------|
| **Confidence** | [get_confidence_range()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#104-121), [get_setup_baseline_floor()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#143-168), [get_adx_confidence_bands()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#245-262), [evaluate_confidence_gates()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#317-420) |
| **Gates** | [get_resolved_gates(phase, setup)](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#767-850), [is_gate_enabled()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#879-892), [get_gate_threshold()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#893-908) |
| **Patterns** | [get_pattern_context()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#913-991), [get_setup_patterns()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#992-1041), [get_setup_validation_modifiers()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#1042-1060) |
| **Strategy** | [get_strategy_horizon_multiplier()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#2118-2140), [get_market_constraints_config()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#1677-1700) |
| **Scoring** | [get_technical_score()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#1933-1940), [get_fundamental_score()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#1941-1947), [calculate_dynamic_confidence_floor()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#1721-1797) |
| **Normalization** | [normalize_threshold()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#2258-2301), [evaluate_threshold()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#2344-2399), [check_metric_threshold()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#1961-2001) |
| **Utility** | [clear_cache()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#2403-2409), [validate_extractor_state()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/query_optimized_extractor.py#2425-2464) |

