## Complete Data Flow: [run_analysis()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/main.py#631-906)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant M as main.py
    participant D as Data Layer
    participant SE as Signal Engine
    participant CH as Config Helpers
    participant CR as Config Resolver
    participant TE as Trade Enhancer

    M->>D: Step 2: compute_fundamentals()
    M->>D: Step 3: compute_indicators_cached() × N horizons
    M->>M: Step 4: Extract macro trend
    M->>SE: Step 5: compute_all_profiles()
    SE->>CH: build_evaluation_context_v5()
    CH->>CR: build_evaluation_context_only()
    CR-->>SE: eval_ctx (setup, strategy, confidence, gates)
    SE-->>M: profiles{} + best_fit
    M->>SE: Step 8: generate_trade_plan()
    SE->>CH: build_evaluation_context_v5()
    SE->>CH: build_execution_context_v5()
    CH->>CR: build_execution_context_from_evaluation()
    CR-->>SE: exec_ctx (entry permission, sizing, risk)
    SE->>TE: enhance_execution_context()
    TE-->>SE: enhanced exec_ctx (real targets, RR, hold time)
    SE->>SE: finalize_trade_decision()
    SE-->>M: trade_plan
    M->>M: Step 9: Save to DB
```

### The 10 Steps of [run_analysis()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/main.py#631-906)

| Step | Action | Key Function |
|------|--------|-------------|
| 1 | Initialize data structure | — |
| 2 | Fetch fundamentals | `compute_fundamentals()` |
| 3 | Compute indicators (per horizon) | `compute_indicators_cached()` |
| 4 | Extract macro trend | `niftyTrendScore` from indicators |
| 5 | Profile scoring | [compute_all_profiles()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/services/signal_engine.py#366-629) → [build_evaluation_context_v5()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/config/config_helpers.py#218-345) |
| 6 | Meta scores (Value/Growth/Quality/Momentum) | `score_*_profile()` |
| 7 | Flatten indicators for display horizon | Dictionary copy |
| 8 | Generate trade plan | [generate_trade_plan()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/services/signal_engine.py#770-1114) → [enhance_execution_context()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/services/trade_enhancer.py#585-753) |
| 9 | Persist to SQLite | [_save_analysis_to_db()](file:///d:/stockviedeo/stock-analyzer-app/main.py#921-1033) |
| 10 | Return analysis_data | Includes profiles, trade_plan, indicators |

